Phuket is Thailand's largest island and its bountiful coastline means that itâs a true haven for those who love seafood. However you can rest assured that if your tastes stray more towards Italian, French, Indian, or even American dishes, that you'll be able to easily find the right restaurant for you.

Food delivery from restaurants near you

The wide variety of cuisine on offer means that you're guaranteed to find the right restaurant to cater to what you're looking for. Whether you're looking for a light breakfast dish, a simple working lunch, or you want to celebrate with a banquet, you're sure to find the perfect place. Choose from the best restaurants in Phuket

You can find anything you want to eat in the province, whether you're looking for tried and tested favourites or a brand new flavour revelation. For example, the Siam Supper Club will be delighted to cook you one of the best steaks you've ever eaten, as will the Sizzle Rooftop Restaurant and Sam's Steak & Grill. If you would like to enjoy some pizza or seafood, why not try the highly rated Surin Chill House? Le Brooklyn Patong would be delighted to serve you up a taste of American or French food, while the Pad Thai Shop or Red Duck Restaurant would be the places to be if you would enjoy a taste of truly authentic Thai cooking. For a taste of the Mediterranean, why not pay a visit to the Da Puccio Restaurant, or step into the Corner Restaurant for a taste of German gourmet.
